WEBVTT

00:00.547 --> 00:03.670
Here are five internet safety tips for kids.

00:04.565 --> 00:08.247
Number one, don't give out personal information,...

00:08.437 --> 00:12.031
...such as home address, school name or phone number.

00:12.471 --> 00:18.369
Number two, never send pictures to strangers.

00:19.677 --> 00:24.777
Number three, keep passwords private except from parents.

00:25.563 --> 00:29.485
Number four, don't download anything without permission.

00:29.819 --> 00:33.041
It may contain a virus that can harm your computer.

00:33.935 --> 00:39.000
And number five, tell an adult if you receive a mean or strange message.

